{"tid":1769873,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"長洲附近1.4級地震","createTime":"2019-12-05T07:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T12:17:49.000Z","uid":154277,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"93244db22553cbc012c72169bf6dd43b3a8242a9","tid":1769873,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:44:45.000Z","msg":"據香港天文台的初步分析，2019年12月5日(星期四)下午12時22分長洲附近發生一次 1.4級地震，震中位於北緯22.20度，東經114.06度附近，即香港天文台之西南約16公里。<br />\n<br />\n香港天文台接獲超過十名市民報告，表示感到這次地震，震動維持數秒。初步分析顯示本港的地震烈度為修訂麥加利地震烈度表的第III (三)度，即室內有感。類似小型貨車駛過的振動。"},{"pid":"10a5dd541a11f6df686f120c92189cd4e545e9a9","tid":1769873,"uid":36049,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"邊個放屁"},{"pid":"3667925264f7ab2e036cf8dbbfd0ddf450ec7e10","tid":1769873,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://www.hko.gov.hk/tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Findex.html&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=812ec168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hko.gov.hk/tc/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"64cc3acf8d05e92735df4fa1f94099b00ac88955","tid":1769873,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c232fd865619dde2b191672ccc417b23bf6dfd02","tid":1769873,"uid":27026,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:46:06.000Z","msg":"天滅港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b8539979bd50a08b0c224a5e98abbc5410502f","tid":1769873,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd47b01bc05223ab406a9f819e0e04ed90e